OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FA man has been convicted of murdering
OL,7,Fhis four-week-old baby son by shaking
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FAtticus Bartlett died in hospital
OL,11,Fafter collapsing at his family home in
OL,12,FChard, Somerset, on July 16 2022.
OL,14,FTony Bartlett, 39, had denied murder
OL,15,Fand an alternative count of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter.
OL,18,FA jury at Bristol Crown Court
OL,19,Funanimously convicted Bartlett,
OL,20,Fformerly a postman, of murder on
OL,21,FWednesday afternoon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
