OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FMr Justice Cavanagh remanded him into
OL,7,Fcustody to be sentenced on July 24.
OL,9,FThe judge said: "There is only one
OL,10,Fsentence for murder, which is a life
OL,11,Fsentence.
OL,13,F"I have to fix a minimum sentence
OL,14,Fbefore the defendant can be considered
OL,15,Ffor release."
OL,17,FMembers of Atticus's family gasped and
OL,18,Fwept in the public gallery of
OL,19,Fcourtroom two after the verdict was
OL,20,Fread out.
OL,26,@qD@QOUuD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FBartlett, appearing by videolink from
OL,7,Fthe dock at Bristol Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt, sobbed loudly.
OL,10,FThe judge thanked jurors for the "care
OL,11,Fand attention" they had given the
OL,12,Fcase, adding that they had served
OL,13,F"magnificently".
OL,15,F"It is clear that you have given this
OL,16,Fvery important case the detailed
OL,17,Fconsideration that it deserves," he
OL,18,Fadded.
OL,20,FHe released them from jury service for
OL,21,Fthe next five years.
OL,26,@rD@bOUsD@NO]uD@AOUuD@OO]wD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
