PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FJurors heard how the attack on Atticus
OL,7,Fmay have been over in seconds.
OL,9,FProsecuting, Charles Row KC said
OL,10,FBartlett had been "drunk and
OL,11,Ffrustrated" when he attacked his
OL,12,Fnewborn son.
OL,14,FBartlett and his then-partner Evelyn
OL,15,FBallentyne, Atticus's mother, had gone
OL,16,Fto a pub and comedy club that evening.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FMs Ballentyne's mother Rachel Donovan
OL,7,Fand her husband Andrew went to the
OL,8,Ffamily home on Darcis Row, Chard, to
OL,9,Fcare for Atticus while his parents
OL,10,Fwere out.
OL,12,FOver the evening, Bartlett drank 8.5
OL,13,Fpints of lager before returning home
OL,14,Fwith Ms Ballentyne.
OL,16,FHe was left alone to feed Atticus in
OL,17,Fthe living room while Ms Ballentyne
OL,18,Fwent upstairs to change at about 11pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FMr Row said: "He would have been
OL,7,Fdisinhibited and therefore more
OL,8,Fcavalier in his handling of Atticus.
OL,10,F"He would have been potentially less
OL,11,Ftolerant, less patient, less able to
OL,12,Fcontrol his temper and frustration."
OL,14,FIt was alleged that, in the short
OL,15,Fperiod of time that Ms Ballentyne was
OL,16,Fupstairs, Bartlett violently shook
OL,17,FAtticus, causing severe internal
OL,18,Finjuries to the baby's brain and
OL,19,Fspinal cord.
OL,26,@nD@NOUrD@AOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FAtticus sustained three rib fractures
OL,7,Fwhich could not be attributed to
OL,8,Fresuscitation efforts.
OL,10,FGiving evidence, Ms Ballentyne
OL,11,Fdescribed coming downstairs and
OL,12,Fhearing Atticus making two loud gasps
OL,13,Fas if he was dying.
OL,15,F"Mr Bartlett can't admit to himself
OL,16,Fthat when he was drunk, in a moment of
OL,17,Fpure violence, he did something that
OL,18,Fhe will regret for the rest of his
OL,19,Flife," Mr Row told jurors.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FDuring the trial, Bartlett insisted he
OL,7,Fhad not harmed his son. His legal team
OL,8,Fsuggested Ms Ballentyne could have
OL,9,Fcaused the fatal injuries.
OL,11,FShe was initially arrested alongside
OL,12,FBartlett but was never charged and
OL,13,Fappeared as a prosecution witness
OL,14,Fduring the trial.
OL,16,FEmergency services attended the
OL,17,Fproperty and Atticus was taken to
OL,18,FMusgrove Park Hospital before being
OL,19,Ftransferred to Bristol Royal Hospital
OL,20,Ffor Children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,FHis brain damage was so severe he did
OL,7,Fnot regain consciousness or breathe
OL,8,Ffor himself.
OL,10,FAtticus died just before midnight on
OL,11,FJuly 23 2022.
OL,13,FAfter the hearing, Detective
OL,14,FSuperintendent Lorett Spierenburg
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is a devastating case in
OL,16,Fwhich a very young baby has lost his
OL,17,Flife as the direct result of a violent
OL,18,Fand cruel act.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,F"The loss of Atticus has had a
OL,7,Fprofound effect on all those who loved
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,F"Tony Bartlett was alone with Atticus
OL,11,Fwhen he suffered these catastrophic
OL,12,Finjuries and the medical evidence
OL,13,Fgathered during the investigation
OL,14,Fproves he was solely responsible for
OL,15,Fcausing them, despite his claims of
OL,16,Finnocence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783705758
OL,3,CFather guilty of murdering four-week-
OL,4,Cold baby
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are very much with
OL,7,FAtticus's family who've had to endure
OL,8,Fa lengthy and complex police
OL,9,Finvestigation, followed by a trial.
OL,10,FThey've shown great dignity and
OL,11,Fcourage throughout."
OL,13,FBartlett, of Axminster, Devon, will be
OL,14,Fsentenced at Bristol Crown Court on
OL,15,FJuly 24.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]
